    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Louis w. Hill, vice president Of\nthe Great Northern railway, arriv-\ned in Spokane yesterday, and said\nthat beside building the V. V. & E.\nto the coast, a line would be run\nconnecting Fernie and Nelson in\nBritish Columbia. On his return\nfrom the coast, Mr.. Hill will re-\nmain over day so as to meet Spo-\nkane business men."
    }
